00:02:52.799 --> 00:03:00.299
Let's talk a little bit about monetization.
We're still at the beginning of this evolution

00:03:00.299 --> 00:03:04.599
of the mobile ecosystem. And I think most
of you probably know this. We saw a very similar

00:03:04.599 --> 00:03:10.439
thing happen with the Web ten years ago.
