00:05:20.940 --> 00:05:27.000
the Midwest. They want to actually pay for
the stuff in your app. Maybe you are producing

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:33.430
a game that has virtual goods that they want
to kind of pay for in an ongoing way. Great.

00:05:33.430 --> 00:05:36.780
That means you can actually do that. You should
just do that. That's a pretty direct way of

00:05:36.780 --> 00:05:40.250
monetizing your app.
