00:05:40.250 --> 00:05:43.930
on the flowchart, you may have another group
of users who are not actually willing to pay

00:05:43.930 --> 00:05:49.060
anything. Maybe they're just sort of browsing
through your app. Maybe it's an RSS reader

00:05:49.060 --> 00:05:53.000
or something. In that case, you should think
about a different business model, in this

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:59.870
case, advertising.
So at Google, we have sort of two major venues

00:05:59.870 --> 00:06:04.000
in which you can monetize your app. One is
the Google Play Store, which Kenneth is going

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:09.500
to cover in-depth in a minute. And the other
is, of course, indirect monetization through

00:06:09.500 --> 00:06:12.010
advertising.
So let's turn it over to Kenneth. And he's

00:06:12.010 --> 00:06:15.140
going to talk about all the different ways
