Before this actually happens, you actually

00:18:37.410 --> 00:18:42.200
make a call to the Google Play -- Again, this
is still on the client. You make a call to

00:18:42.200 --> 00:18:46.550
the Google Play client to see what type of
billing is supported and what version.

00:18:46.550 --> 00:18:51.490
After you do that, after you check that you
