00:21:23.000 --> 00:21:29.630
in-app notify. So once you've processed the
transaction and you say -- let's you made

00:21:29.630 --> 00:21:33.380
it available to the user, you want to make
sure that you respond to that notification

00:21:33.380 --> 00:21:38.520
